Concept:

electropacker cli tool

Commands

init [:path]
build {type:}[main|renderer]
start {:env}[development|production]
dist

descriptions:

init: initializes the directory structure for the main and renderer process using current configuration.
  Creates folder structure for main and renderer electron processes.
    default:
   src/
   |
   |——main/
   |  |--main.js
   |  |——webpack.config.js
   |
   |——renderer/
      |--main.js
      |——webpack.config.js

Options
--config
--override-webpack :[main|renderer]
--debug
--help

JSON configuration default:

{
  "main.src": "src/main",
  "main.webpack.config": "webpack.config.js",
  "main.webpack.override": false
  "renderer.src": "src/renderer",
  "renderer.webpack.config": "webpack.config.js",
  "renderer.webpack.override": false
}

Example ussage:

electropacker init
electropacker build
electropacker build main or electronpacker build Renderer
electropacker start development
electropacker start production
electropacker dist

or

epak init
